  L<Git::SVN>.
  
  C<Git::SVN::Ra> has not been tested using callers other than
  B<git-svn> itself.
  
  =head1 SEE ALSO
  
  L<SVN::Ra>.
  
  =head1 INCOMPATIBILITIES
  
  None reported.
  
  =head1 BUGS
  
  None.
